        <h2>Introduce</h2>
        <p>
            Shanghai Star International (SSI) is a company specializing in the following products
            of the Spacer bar for Insulating Glass and also<br />
            trades in Sealant and Molecular Sieve for Insulating Glass.</p>
        <p>
            <b>Aluminium Spacer Bars and Connectors</b> - This covers a range of 5.5mm to 24mm Aluminium
            Spacer Bars for Standard as well as<br />
            Bendable applications.</p>
        <p>
            <b>Plastic Spacer Bars and Connectors</b> - This covers a range of 5.5mm to 24mm Warm Spacer
            bar for Insulating Glass.</p>
        <p>
            <b>Molecular Sieves (Dessicants)</b> - Molecular Sieves are used for Insulated Glass Units
            are available in 3 different bead sizes.</p>
        <p>
            Except the above products, We still have the polysulphide sealant, butyl sealant,
            silicone sealant for Insulating Glass.</p>
